":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T08:05:25.000Z","msg":"點會難只要加入民族黨，去美領事館前面大叫「民族黨員XXX香港獨立」，叫到差佬即刻入領事館申請政治庇護<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932679972a7b762dd1340262063732059d053646","tid":858721,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:45:18.000Z","msg":"到時候商家佬出嚟嘈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就係革命嘅開端"},{"pid":"f3dbfa93165b694d0cd7cf2c55d1eae64a019a4b","tid":858721,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:48:24.000Z","msg":"唔好亂用「港人」<br />\n<br />\n香港人就好多有唔同既國籍<br />\n<br />\n係得支那籍先出事"},{"pid":"055a660a2c37e5eabeed03b043dcbe72227b8ef8","tid":858721,"uid":202139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T21:54:46.000Z","msg":"所以我讀POLYU SPEED都唔讀VTC RMIT"},{"pid":"d4fd085a5b4a81b8e00c02dc4344b11296ba62ac","tid":858721,"uid":42435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T01:34:27.000Z","msg":"最大檸樂簽証方面，個D平日舐共最落力個班，以後攞美國簽證等同大陸＂有背景＂支那人，重有本特衰護照，兵敗如山倒，好多國家可能當支那護照，取消免簽證，因為香港沒有獨特角色，祇係支那一個城市"},{"pid":"98723c9f29eda69c0de999870b75ef78aa5c9a14","tid":858721,"uid":29914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T02:36:25.000Z","msg":"快撚啲取消啦屌"}]}